{"tid":328547,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台爆] 開電風扇吹散洩漏氣體觸發火花   逢甲夜市煤氣爆炸1死15傷","createTime":"2017-07-19T16:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T16:15:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc5232a02a62d9e8aae037ae440914888ce9a0b9","tid":328547,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170719/large/19cb2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170719%2Flarge%2F19cb2p.jpg&h=e69ae154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170719/large/a1401a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170719%2Flarge%2Fa1401a.gif&h=e536b231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年訪人次逾1,300萬的港人遊台熱點台中市逢甲夜市商圈，昨日中午發生駭人的爆炸事故，最少造成1死15傷。初步消息指，第一天上班的煤氣工程人員幫西安街心齋橋餐廳更換煤氣罐時發生洩漏意外，事後煤氣店老闆用電風扇吹散煤氣時產生火花引發爆炸，餐廳負責人及煤氣店老闆首當其衝，九成燒傷。台灣消防在事發後巡查餐廳樓上的住宅，更發現一具女性的燒焦屍體，初步相信死者是一名19歲姓陳、就讀逢甲大學的女學生。<br />\n<br />\n事發在昨午約12時許，餐廳負責人吳豪邦聞到店舖有濃烈煤氣味，通知煤氣店協助，店方派出第一天上班的工人林坤榮前來更換煤氣罐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170719/large/a1401b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170719%2Flarge%2Fa1401b.gif&h=6bb9b5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170719/large/a1401c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170719%2Flarge%2Fa1401c.gif&h=a713b54c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消防事後發現，煤氣爆炸造成三店舖全毀，另有十間店舖損毀嚴重，外牆熏得全黑，滿地都是玻璃與爆裂的瓷磚，一片頹垣敗瓦。依據市府初步調查，起火的餐廳，包括建築物、營業登記與消防設施都通過檢驗，沒有違規營業情況。<br />\n<br />\n逢甲夜市是全台中最大夜市，約有2,200間店舖，是香港旅客到台中的必到地點，去年該處一共有1,300萬人次前往，平日每日亦有平均2.1萬人次。"},{"pid":"70976b029a21fd1dcc23ada90951aee3a2d1ae98","tid":328547,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"世界大戰即將開始！<br />\n<br />\n連登仔將全面進場!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820741ae8c7251a11f6ef8850fbd49d51f2cdb0f","tid":328547,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世界大戰即將開始！<br />\n<br />\n連登仔將全面進場!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港國民 VS 崇台踩港撚<br />\n<br />\nRound 34"}]}